  "content": "  <span class=\"highlight-red\">No Code Review.</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"slide-subtitle\" style=\"font-size: 22px; margin-bottom: 32px;\">\n    I'm building a Rust project solo. No team. No PR reviews.<br>\n    The bugs I was shipping had a pattern.\n  </div>\n  <!-- Bug examples -->\n  <div class=\"card\" style=\"border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-red); padding: 28px;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent-red); margin-bottom: 16px;\">Bugs That Shipped</div>\n    <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px;\">\n      <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 16px;\">\n        <div style=\"font-size: 24px; flex-shrink: 0;\">&#10060;</div>\n        <div>\n          <div style=\"font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700;\">Config typo silently swallowed</div>\n          <div style=\"font-size: 18px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 4px;\">A wildcard match caught all strings. Misspell a retriever name and it just... works, doing nothing.</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 16px;\">\n        <div style=\"font-size: 24px; flex-shrink: 0;\">&#10060;</div>\n        <div>\n          <div style=\"font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700;\">CLI returned success on failure</div>\n          <div style=\"font-size: 18px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 4px;\">Server unreachable? Exit code 0. Looked like success in every CI pipeline.</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 16px;\">\n        <div style=\"font-size: 24px; flex-shrink: 0;\">&#10060;</div>\n        <div>\n          <div style=\"font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700;\">Race condition in log rotation</div>\n          <div style=\"font-size: 18px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 4px;\">Size check was outside the mutex. A TOCTOU race that passed every test.</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 16px;\">\n        <div style=\"font-size: 24px; flex-shrink: 0;\">&#10060;</div>\n        <div>\n          <div style=\"font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700;\">DoS vector in dashboard</div>",
